transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Haan sir, woh mai yeh bol rahi thi ki jo video make ke liye puch rahi thi mai.
Customer: Awaaz nahi hai toh.
Executive: Abhi connect karte hai.
Customer: Bhej du?
Executive: Abhi connect karte hai na matlab aap link bhej do.
Executive: Haan wahi keh rahi hu mai bhej du ki?
Customer: Haan link bhi change kar do aur mere ko link change kar do.
Executive: Theek hai mai whatsapp pe link share kar rahi hu aapko.
Customer: Haan haan kar do kar do.
summary:

- Customer wants to send a video link.



Resolution:

- Executive agreed to receive the link on WhatsApp.
